sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API as Search API
    participant RC as Result Cache
    participant Geo as Geo Index
    participant Biz as Business Store
    participant CDC as CDC / Update Bus

    Note over C,Biz: SEARCH (read path)
    C->>API: GET /search?lat,lng,radius,category
    API->>API: compute geohash prefix at radius precision
    API->>RC: lookup (geohash_prefix, category)
    alt cache hit
        RC-->>API: cached page
        API-->>C: results
    else miss
        API->>Geo: fetch candidates in cell + 8 neighbors
        Geo-->>API: candidate biz_ids
        API->>Biz: hydrate metadata
        Biz-->>API: business records
        API->>API: haversine filter by radius
        API->>API: apply category filter
        API->>API: sort by distance/rating, paginate
        API->>RC: store page (TTL 60s)
        API-->>C: results
    end

    Note over Biz,Geo: WRITE PATH (CRUD sync)
    Biz-)CDC: business updated event
    CDC-)Geo: update spatial index entry
